When Professor Joseph taught the course back in Spring 2016, he had a final, as per https://inst.eecs.berkeley.edu/~cs162/sp16/.

He also taught the course in Fall 2016, when he did not have a final, as per https://inst.eecs.berkeley.edu/~cs162/fa16/.

Therefore, its quite ambiguous. Since the latest version taught by him does not have a final, you could assume that there would not be a final for next semester too but again, the best thing to do is to email and clarify with the professor himself..
